LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:CES"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

),
 the task-level heterogeneity results in a CES function with aggregate human labor and aggregate AI labor as input (i.e.,
 Equation 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:CES_desired"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

).
